{"tid":710442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"是日辯題：廢老係唔係今日社會既問題？","createTime":"2018-06-20T18:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T03:12:31.000Z","uid":45148,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53e3edfb383cc0f370d596c2a49ca9fef4e2fdc6","tid":710442,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T18:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/020643_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F020643_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=1840db89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會員質疑廢老唔係搞到年青人無屋住<br />\n但最後佢竟然都指責家中廢老<br />\n<br />\n點解佢唔問自己：宜家係廢老搞到你濕疹咩<br />\n<br />\n根本就自相矛盾<br />\n記得佢講：濕疹生仔仆街過窮人生仔<br />\n究竟佢知唔知窮人，公屋仔既慘況<br />\n自己住私樓就唔知民間疾苦，離地到呢<br />\n淨係你濕疹就好慘？<br />\n<br />\n而且好多時跳樓自殺都係私樓仔，<br />\ne.g.副局長個仔<br />\n應該罰下班私樓仔住劏房<br />\n感受下咩叫民不聊生"},{"pid":"892fad22ffd30249254057f077da9f8543d66ab0","tid":710442,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}